lg.head:
{@sūcīpatra
svargārohaṇa parba
biṣaẏa pr̥ṣṭhāṅka@}

div.head:
{@suhāṇī kanyā śikhareśvara śiba sebāre niyukta,
gaurī gopāḷuṇī beśe kr̥ttibāsa o
kīrttibāsa daityaṅku saṁhāra@}

lg.head:
{@śvāna rūpe dharmaṅkara prabeśa, yudhiṣṭhi raṅkara
indraṅka staba, byāghra darśana o
kaḷiyugara niryātanā@}

{@pariśiṣṭa
‘cha’ pothi pāṭha@}
(tat saṅge saṅge jha, ḍa, ka, tha, ṇa, ṭa, ṭha–pothire acchi)

div.head:
{@25 pr̥ṣṭhāre thibā pāthāntarara–“ẏe kanyā yogaru tuhi
tarilu bahana”–ehi pada pare ‘cha’ pothire
saṁkṣipta mahābhārathaacchi |@}
